<h4 id="examples">Examples</h4>
<ol>
  <li>create a file named hello.txt with the following content.</li>
</ol>

<div class="language-cmake highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nb">message</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">"Hello world!"</span><span class="p">)</span>         <span class="c1"># A message to print</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<ol>
  <li>run the script</li>
</ol>

<div class="language-shell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>cmake <span class="nt">-P</span> hello.txt
</code></pre></div></div>

